    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1895-10-26T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1895-10-26T00:00:00-05:00" n="155" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d155">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Sill</persName> to Mr.
                                    <persName type="to">Olney</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Seoul</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1895-10-26">
                            <hi rend="italic">October 26,
                                1895</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Japanese minister and officers of his legation and army have been sent to
                            Japan. Count Inoye is coming to Seoul as special ambassador. The King is
                            under strict duress. His life in peril. I do not recognize decrees
                            forced from him. Allen’s conduct of affairs excellent.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Sill.</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
